data.description: Looking for a large house for your big family?? Are you looking for a big yard for the kids to run around or to entertain?? Then come see this upgraded and spacious 5 bedroom and 2.5 bath home with a formal living and dining room, family room, plus an additional living space on the second level. Eat-in kitchen with breakfast bar offers a free standing electric range plus dual built-in ovens and a large pantry. All bedrooms are on the upper level. The property backs to a greenbelt with no neighbors behind. Close proximity to IH35, major retailers and restaurants. Come see you new home!!
